\begin_layout Section
Inertial confinement fusion
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The concept of using lasers to trap a plasma within an imploding, ablatively-dri
ven shell at sufficiently high pressure to allow for the occurrence of fusion
 reactions was first articulated by Nuckolls in 1972 
