LatexCommand citep
key "Nuckolls1972"
literal "false"

\end_inset

, just over a decade after the invention of the laser.
 This fundmental idea has remained unchanged in the 50 subsequent years
 of inertial confinement fusion research, although some related approaches
 incorporate strong magnetic fields to aid in confinement, or particle beams
 to assist with plasma ignition.
 
