\begin_inset Formula $\omega(r,z)=\frac{\Gamma}{\pi a^{2}}\exp\left(-(z^{2}+(r-R)^{2})/a^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

 and solution of the Poisson equation for the streamfunction 
\begin_inset Formula $\laplacian\psi=-\omega$
\end_inset

, with 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{u}=\curl\psi$
\end_inset

.
